Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.35,0:01:38.00,Top,,0,0,0,,Ah... So the semester is finally ending?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.00,0:01:42.85,Top,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow evening, we'll already be in London, \Ndining with Dad and Mum.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, give way!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.84,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Janet will fluff all the blankets \Nin Room Seven for you! {lit: will blow away all the dust - chatgpt says "fluff" is the right word to use with that swatter-like thing she has, but idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.60,0:01:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.18,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.69,0:02:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My paper flowers! {lit: paper decorations}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for them since last year! {lit: for six months}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My notebook too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.13,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,General cleanup brings out all sorts of stuff. {??? dunno what she means, maybe "all thanks to ..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious history notebook.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.82,0:02:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Is that Miss Kennedy's handwriting? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I submitted my homework, \Nshe even wrote this to praise me! {?? I assume what they're seeing there is some elaborate praise for well done homework}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about the life of Cleopatra. {lit: the story of cleopatra - i assume that's what the homework was about??}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy is really \Nfond of me as her student! {/favours/partial}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's not just you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.25,0:02:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My Greek mythology notebook \Nalso looks like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.73,0:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! So many notes!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And she lent me Da Vinci's art book. {book of pictures (paintings, drawings, etc.); collection of pictures}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy cares for each student \Nas if they were her only one.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.81,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Speak of the devil, \Nthere's Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! {can't think of a way to avoid it here}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.69,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't hear us.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.84,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she was up all night \Nwriting her paper again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear \Nabout Miss Kennedy, Belinda?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.64,0:03:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did. Miss Kennedy
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.61,0:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was only meant to stand in for Miss Lewis, \Nwho was on sick leave for a long time, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... What is it about Miss Kennedy?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Very bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.33,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Miss Kennedy \Nwill have to leave St. Clare's!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I read it, \Nit's a great thesis. {/paper}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.31,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy, you must guard this with your life.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress, can we talk?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress! {???? sensei maybe? also could refer to kenny here}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.42,0:03:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're letting Miss Kennedy go?! {oidasu = kick/drive out - in japanese it's softer than in english so not sure what word to choose}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, girls! \NI'm having a guest, mind you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.87,0:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.80,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to ruin the thesis Miss Kennedy \Nspent five years writing in just five seconds?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... W-We're sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Professor Sydney of Oxford University. {not in the book}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.22,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The professor came here today from London \Nto accompany Miss Kennedy. {/take with him/pick up}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This thesis was met with great praise.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.73,0:04:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy has been officially invited \Nto be a female professor at Oxford University.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At Oxford?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So that rumour that you're letting her go... {oidasu}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I {\i1}am{\i0} letting her go. {oidasu}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With honours and my gratitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.92,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy did a wonderful job \Nreplacing Miss Lewis for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.05,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for her to nourish \Nher own talents too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If she carries on her research at Oxford,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy will gain international recognition in no time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really have to leave...? {lit: really goodbye?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.40,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the time you spent with Miss Kennedy \Na lifelong source of pride. {lit: may what she taught you be your pride for life}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.31,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it’s they who shaped me, \Na clumsy novice teacher, into who I am now… {/supported me}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.62,0:05:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Janet, Kathleen,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.46,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and each and every one of you, \Nwho opened your heart to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing you... {/the fact I met you}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,will be my lifelong source of pride.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Miss Kennedy!}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.52,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress, would you please \Ngrant me this final request?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to give a lesson just one more time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I can teach them now... No!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just a fraction, \NI want to share it with them once more. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the weather wonderful?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A lesson that'll become your heart's memento?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Give it in our rose garden. {lit: make the rose garden your classroom.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.79,0:06:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell all the first formers that the final lesson \Nwill be held there after school today.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.89,0:06:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"If she carries on her research at Oxford, \NMiss Kennedy will
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.21,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,gain international recognition in no time!"
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.75,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful! {suteki?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get her autograph!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll have something to show to our relatives when we get home!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.02,0:07:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, an autograph! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.75,0:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.22,0:07:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A Rolls-Royce!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.57,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're loading Miss Kennedy's \Nluggage in it already.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.07,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels as if Miss Kennedy has suddenly become \Nso distant from us somehow. {/estranged}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heavy, so be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crumbs! {/that's right/I know}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.19,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s too painful to think \Nthat we’ll never see Miss Kennedy again!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be coming to that final class...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,lest I burst into tears!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've invited you over for tea \Nseveral times, haven't I? {??? idk why she says that}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our secret. {/in secret}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But our secret meetings are no more.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not before we do it once more. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.34,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Patricia, are you free now?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.82,0:08:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world did she go?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one feeling lonely, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands up!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you... {??? yatta wa ne?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.56,0:09:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Didn't I tell you to behave yourselves?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.19,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to stay in this school's good graces \Nto get what we came for! {lit: if people of this school hate us, our wishes won't come true}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.83,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.77,0:09:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologise now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.77,0:09:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, who might you be?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to ask you something.\NHow do we get to the headmistress's room? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.57,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ah, well, if you go around that building... {? not sure what's mune here}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NWe're leaving!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are those kids?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.13,0:09:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what an adorable girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be about your age in that photo.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to me is Miss Marple. {not in book}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.67,0:10:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She was like a big tree of wisdom \Nwith big boughs branching in all directions.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As a student, I was a very docile girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Many teachers even struggled \Nto remember my name.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.92,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, Miss Marple called out to me, \Nalone as usual, and lent me a book.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.92,0:10:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd talk about history and literature for hours, \Nlosing all sense of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.36,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When she saw how much it made my eyes shine, \Nshe'd do it every day since then.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.17,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She taught me the joy of learning and made me want to learn more and more about all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never get enough. {/more and more}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.81,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a day goes by that I don’t thank God \Nfor that wonderful encounter with Miss Marple.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If Miss Marple hadn’t been there for me,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.65,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I might never have developed a passion for research \Nor ended up in this delightful job.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the one who gently opened
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.86,0:11:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the door to a passion for knowledge \Nthat lay dormant in my young heart. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,Passion for knowledge? {lit: The door to knowledge}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell's bells! This school is huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all like the one we go to. {lit: completely different from the [one in our] village}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just as labyrinthine! {/complicated }
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they need all these stairs for?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is, the headmistress's room.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.32,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember? Our destiny is at stake!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.72,0:11:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But that room is...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallo!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come from St. Mary's Island. {we hear "sento miria" but everything else indicates that it's actually https://maps.app.goo.gl/JEcQ93zYRyR4X6Mp8 - although maybe they invented a new island, based on it, or simply misread "mary"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a favour.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.60,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help us find our teacher, Headmistress!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for our teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.87,0:12:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our old teacher has died.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in heaven now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we came here on a ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys came here all on your own?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.37,0:12:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We left early this morning \Nand it took us half a day to get here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re starving like wolves now!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now stop for a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, \Nthis isn't the headmistress.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I understood from this—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.22,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you kids are seriously in distress \Nand you've been through a lot. {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? {dunno what he means by "true?" true what? that she understood?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.16,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Mary's Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty far... {lit: Distant island}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it only has ninety people. {/the population is 90}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninety-two.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My younger brothers were born the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're twins, just like these two!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.25,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one school on the island, \Nwith only eighteen students studying there,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and only one teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.68,0:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that one teacher died of illness?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.15,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sent letters to all the nearby schools, \Nasking them to recommend a teacher to us. {/to all schools here and there, asking to introduce us to a teacher}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dozens of them, I tell ya! {letters}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you get an answer?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They all refused. {lit: all "no"}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.41,0:13:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't bear it, couldn't sit still, \Nso we came to ask personally.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.18,0:13:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told that the headmistress \Nof St. Clare's is a person of great compassion. {/very kind}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.07,0:13:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, we've received a letter \Nfrom St. Mary's Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.28,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.31,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we at St. Clare's \Ndon't have a teacher that'd fit the bill.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I replied to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do something about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.86,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received a call \Nfrom the mayor of St. Mary's Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.43,0:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to know if any of the children from their island had ended up here. {??? no clue what's that kochira ni omowasu shimasu, probably "he asked me"}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallo?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mary... I finally found you! \NHow could you sneak out like that? {lit: fleeing the island silently}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all deathly worried!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must find a new teacher no matter what...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You return to the island this instant!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to the mainland to pick you up. {lit: halfway through/midway - dunno how else that could work unless he means he'll come to the mainland port to meet her}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.52,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch over the children \Nand see to it that they return safely.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.79,0:14:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you kids must go home now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Matron to walk you to the station.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.10,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll also ask around through my contacts \Nand other schools once more.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.14,0:14:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put in my best effort \Nto come back to you with good news.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.73,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy, everyone has gathered \Nat the Rose Garden.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.00,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else will ever come to our island!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Never... Never again! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That teacher we saw earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.43,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask... \NAsk that lady once more!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.88,0:15:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us begin...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the final lesson.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be something important.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.91,0:15:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme! {this is where dildoman gave up on this show on 15.09.2025 - genuinely have to wonder if they simply couldn't get their hands on any more books after the first, so they simply started winding it and stopped caring... kinda sad, this show was just mid up to this episode, not totally terrible. It was a good run. - Paul}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.06,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you again! \Nwhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's Miss Kennedy's precious thesis!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a disaster, Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thesis...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.76,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'm not going to scold you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll scold us for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.16,0:16:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She totally will!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy will probably be beside herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Open! Open up now!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up already!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jim, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.49,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's gonna fall!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, call the police \Nand ask for help!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim's mother... \NPlease, protect Jim from heaven above.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim's mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell ill and died.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is she that teacher from the island?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, what should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still! I'm going now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.82,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.58,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I only... Only...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanted a teacher for the island.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With a teacher, I might be able to learn to read. {LMAOOOOOOOOOOOOOO yeah they fucking went out at this point, a teacher's son who can't read in elementary school, sure; I wonder if that's some kind of "anime about twins curse" where it turns complete dogshit in episode 13}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.90,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because right now
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.57,0:17:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,there are so many letters from mother \Nthat I can't read.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother's letters?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The world-acclaimed thesis! {/Worldwide paper}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can write that thesis again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.42,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you only have one letter from your mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.97,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you want, \NI can read this for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As a sign that I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim has never shown it to anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.72,0:18:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"My Jim, it pains my heart, \Nbut I'll have to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum has to go to heaven.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As the only teacher on a small island,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.50,0:18:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I had many more things yet to teach you, \NMary, Tom, and everyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.37,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The history of our country, \Nthe workings of life on our planet,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the preciousness of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.02,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without me, \NI'm sure your new teacher will..."
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.97,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.92,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jim, it's all right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum... {I wanna punch him in the face so hard he'd have a hole in his head, who the fuck ever thought this was a good idea}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jim, let me tell you something good.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave this school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll go to the island with you all!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.61,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miss Kennedy...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! Would you approve \Nof me becoming your new teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.45,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NSurely, that can't be true!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy already agreed to go to Oxford!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.51,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Miss Kennedy makes a promise, \Nshe never takes it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.11,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She picked up that terrifying stubbornness from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's just...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing through!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.68,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're really going to that remote place?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.76,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you went to Oxford, you could become a world-famous researcher.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It occurred to me the moment I saw these children:
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.87,0:21:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this is my chance to open the door to the passion for knowledge, lying dormant in their hearts.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.41,0:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Miss Marple did for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.45,0:21:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for all the wonderful acquaintances I've made.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kennedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.39,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be well.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.41,0:21:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.38,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.75,0:21:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the final lesson got cancelled.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.02,0:21:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the lesson did take place.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.79,0:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she left, Miss Kennedy \Ntaught us this amazing way of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.13,0:22:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home now. \NDad and Mum are waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tell them about the wonderful Miss Kennedy.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.56,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From what point?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.37,0:23:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our cousin Alison will be enrolling at St. Clare's for the new semester. {alright, so I guess they did have other books? then I have no other explanation other that the whole fucking studio decided to have a collective stroke that week}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.18,0:23:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alison is still as dry as ever \Nand only thinks about herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.37,0:23:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that gets to her head.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.88,0:23:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she have to follow in our footsteps?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:49.58,0:23:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A fun new semester...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.86,0:23:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to turn messy because of Alison, \Nbut will we stand for it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.87,0:23:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But when a senior girl sent for her, \Nshe did the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.30,0:23:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twins at St. Clare's:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Homework is Burned!" {宿題を燃やしちゃった!}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.32,0:24:03.76,Note,,0,0,0,,Episode 14 \NThe Homework is Burned! {宿題を燃やしちゃった!}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.27,0:24:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
